    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Periodicals, reports, or essays giving critical estimates and appraisals of art, a performance, or event. For other critical descriptions and analyses, prefer "criticism."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
